# run solution.py on samples
import subprocess, sys, textwrap

def run_input(inp):
    p = subprocess.Popen(["/opt/openhands-venv/bin/python3","solution.py"], stdin=subprocess.PIPE, stdout=subprocess.PIPE, stderr=subprocess.PIPE, text=True)
    out, err = p.communicate(inp)
    return p.returncode, out, err

samples = [
    ("4\n1 2 5 3\n", "5\n"),
    ("7\n3 1 4 1 5 9 2\n", "14\n"),
    ("5\n1 1 1 1 1\n", "0\n"),
]
for inp, exp in samples:
    rc, out, err = run_input(inp)
    print('rc=',rc,'out=',out,'expected=',exp,'err=',err)
